volumeInfo.subtitle: Link Your Apps and Web Services Using RestKit
volumeInfo.description: A step-by-step, example-based guide to learning how you can link your apps and web services using RestKit.This book is for iOS developers of all levels who are interested in boosting their productivity by utilizing third party libraries and who have a willingness to learn how to build RESTful apps using the RestKit framework. A basic knowledge of Objective-C is required as well as a simple understanding of how to use CoreData.
volumeInfo.title: RestKit for IOS
